room_title: Escape room "The Chocolate Factory" by Escape Now Houston in Houston
room_description: The Chocolate factory closed its doors to visitors many years ago, leaving everyone wondering what really goes on behind closed doors. Rumors say that inside the secret chocolate recipe is hidden. Out of the blue, one lucky day the owner decides to hold a lottery to win a chance to visit the factory. You have an hour to find the golden ticket and escape with the recipe!
